\c 12
\s Madzimambo akakundwa naIsraeri
\p
\v 1 Zvino awa madzimambo enyika, vana vaIsraeri avakarova ndokugara nhaka yenyika yavo mhiri kwaJoridhani kumabvazuva, kubva pamupata weArinoni kusvika pagomo reHerimoni, nebani rese kumabvazuva:
\v 2 Sihoni mambo weVaAmori, waigara paHeshibhoni, waitonga kubva paAroeri riri pamahombekombe erwizi Arinoni uye pakati perwizi, nehafu yeGiriyadhi, kusvikawo kurwizi Jabhoki, mucheto wevana vaAmoni,
\v 3 uye bani kusvika kugungwa reKineroti kumabvazuva, uye kusvika pagungwa rebani, Gungwa reMunyu kumabvazuva, nzira yeBhetijeshimoti, uye kubva kuchamhembe pazasi peAshidhodhi-Pisiga;
\v 4 nemuganhu waOgi mambo weBhashani, wevakasiiwa veVaRegaimu vaigara paAshitaroti nepaEdhirei,
\v 5 wakatonga pagomo reHerimoni nepaSarika nepaBhashani rese, kusvika kumuganhu wevaGeshuri nevaMaakati, nehafu yeGiriyadhi, muganhu yaSihoni, mambo weHeshibhoni.
\v 6 Mozisi muranda waJehovha, nevana vaIsraeri vakavarova; Mozisi muranda waJehovha ndokuipa vaRubheni nevaGadhi, nehafu yerudzi rwaManase, kuti ive yavo.
\p
\v 7 Zvino awa madzimambo enyika Joshua nevana vaIsraeri yavakarova nechekuno kwaJoridhani kumavirazuva, kubva paBhaari-Gadhi mumupata weRebhanoni, kusvikira pagomo reHaraki rinokwira kuSeiri; Joshua yaakapa kumarudzi aIsraeri kuva nhaka zvichienderana nekuparadzaniswa kwavo.
\v 8 Panyika yezvikomo, nemumipata, nemumapani, nemuzvitubu, nemurenje, nechamhembe: VaHiti, VaAmori, neVaKenani, VaPerezi, VaHivhi, neVaJebhusi,
\v 9 mambo weJeriko, umwe; mambo weAi, padivi peBheteri, umwe;
\v 10 mambo weJerusarema, umwe; mambo weHebhuroni, umwe;
\v 11 mambo weJarimuti, umwe; mambo weRakishi, umwe;
\v 12 mambo weEgironi, umwe; mambo weGezeri umwe;
\v 13 mambo weDhebhiri, umwe; mambo Gedheri, umwe;
\v 14 mambo weHorima, umwe; mambo weAradhi, umwe;
\v 15 mambo weRibhina, umwe, mambo weAdhuramu, umwe;
\v 16 mambo weMakedha, umwe; mambo weBheteri, umwe;
\v 17 mambo weTapua, umwe, mambo weHeferi, umwe;
\v 18 mambo weAfeki, umwe; mambo weRasharoni, umwe;
\v 19 mambo weMadhoni, umwe; mambo weHazori, umwe;
\v 20 mambo weShimironi-meroni, umwe; mambo weAkishafi, umwe;
\v 21 mambo weTaanaki, umwe; mambo weMegidho, umwe;
\v 22 mambo weKedheshi, umwe; mambo weJokineamu paKarimeri, umwe;
\v 23 mambo weDhori pamuganhu weDhori, umwe; mambo weGoimi paGirigari, umwe;
\v 24 mambo weTiriza, umwe; madzimambo ese aiva makumi matatu neumwe.